        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>National Critical Capabilities Defense Act of </b><strong>2021</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes the Committee on National Critical Capabilities to review certain transactions by U.S. businesses, including those transactions that could result in an unacceptable risk to national critical capabilities. Further, the bill authorizes the President to suspend or prohibit transactions that pose an unacceptable risk to national critical capabilities.</p>]]>
        </text>
